rd and soft skills. Example Attorney requirements J.D. degree is required Research, writing, and analytical skills 3+ Years of litigation experience Admitted to the state bar of current residence Negotiation skills and experience Written and verbal communication skills Attorney related job titles: Lawyer Counsel Barrister Attorney-At-Law Legal Adviser Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
